videos.description: TJ Holyfield goes up for a layup, but Kansas State's Xavier Sneed comes from behind to block the shot with authority off the backboard.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Sneed swats shot off glass for massive rejection) 2020/01/14

videos.headline: Sneed swats shot off glass for massive rejection

videos.description: Kansas State coach Bruce Weber is assessed a technical foul after arguing with a referee about a charging call that he felt should have been a blocking foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Coach Weber T'd up for arguing with ref) 2020/01/14

videos.headline: Coach Weber T'd up for arguing with ref

videos.description: Texas Tech's Kyler Edwards gets his defender off-balance with a hesitation then drives to the rim for the easy lay-in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Edwards uses sweet hesitation move to score) 2020/01/14
